===Blackpool===
*[[Football League Fourth Division|Fourth Division]] playoff winners: [[1991-92 in English football|1991/92]]

===Grimsby Town===
*Grimsby Town Supporters Player of the Year: [[1995-96 in English football|1995/96]], [[1998-99 in English football|1998/99]]
*[[Football League Trophy|Auto Windscreens Shield]] winner: [[1997-98 in English football|1997/98]]
*[[Football League Second Division|Second Division]] playoff winner: [[1997-98 in English football|1997/98]]

===Leicester Masters===
*Central Masters Player of the Tournament: 2005
*Masters Cup winner: 2005
*Coventry Masters Golden Boot Winner: 2007
*Coventry Masters Winners: 2007

